Package edu.ncsu.csc.CoffeeMaker.models

Class Recipe

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc.CoffeeMaker.models.DomainObject
      • edu.ncsu.csc.CoffeeMaker.models.Recipe
  • @Entity
public class Recipe
extends DomainObject
    Recipe for the coffee maker. Recipe is tied to the database using Hibernate libraries. See RecipeRepository and RecipeService for the other two pieces used for database support.
    Author:
    Kai Presler-Marshall
